# Autonomous execution permanence phase

struktur AutonomousExecutionPermanence
    permanent_execution_generations
    stabilized_execution_permanence
    verified_permanence_cycles
slutt

struktur RecursiveCompilerPermanence
    recursive_compiler_generations
